  "texts": [
    "Finally, FL can help increase the model's generalization capacity by allowing it to learn from a varied variety of data sources and adapt to different distributions and biases in the data.",
    "This can be particularly useful when the data is not very diverse or is biased in some way.",
    "Overall, while the performance of an ML model is typically related to the amount of data it is trained on, FL can still provide benefits in terms of scalability, privacy, and generalization, even when the training data is not particularly large.",
    "Feature ExtractionTwo separate strategies were used to extract features from the faces observed by YOLO: a texture-based analysis tool and a SegCaps-CNN-based method.",
    "The integration of both texture-based analysis and the SegCaps-CNN-based method for feature extraction in the YOLO-based face recognition system stems from their complementary strengths."
